WEBVTT

00:01:29.924 --> 00:01:32.627
Or, to say that in another way,

00:01:32.651 --> 00:01:36.402
what does it mean to be an AI
in the 21st century?

00:01:37.441 --> 00:01:39.538
Any android or AI machine

00:01:39.562 --> 00:01:42.679
is only intelligent
as long as we collaborate with it.

00:01:43.327 --> 00:01:44.792
It can construct things

00:01:44.816 --> 00:01:48.072
that human intelligence intends to produce

00:01:48.096 --> 00:01:50.238
but does not have the capacity to do so.

00:01:51.373 --> 00:01:55.178
Think about your activities
and social networks, for example.

00:01:55.208 --> 00:01:58.756
They get smarter
the more you interact with them.

